text: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, JUNE 21, 12-2PM. Nestled on an expansive .69-acre lot in the prestigious Shady Oaks neighborhood, this stunning estate offers an unparalleled lifestyle with a million-dollar backyard oasis. Located within award-winning Carroll ISD, the residence is the epitome of luxury & sophistication. A grand 32-foot foyer with a sweeping curved staircase sets the tone, opening to an airy & bright family room with soaring 20-foot ceilings, a dramatic stone fireplace, & a wall of windows that frame the resort-style backyard. The chef's kitchen is a culinary dream, boasting a 6-burner cooktop, built-in refrigerator, double ovens, oversized island, & seamless flow to the family & breakfast rooms. The serene primary suite is a true retreat featuring coffered ceilings, garden tub, walk-through shower, dual custom closets, & panoramic views of the lush outdoor sanctuary. The main level also includes a formal dining room with built-ins, a recessed wine room, butlers pantry, private study, large guest suite, spacious utility room with island, mudroom, powder room, & a full bath with pool accessall complemented by hand-scraped hardwood flooring. Upstairs, enjoy a vaulted game room with scenic views, an oversized home theater -equipment included- with wet bar & beverage fridge, plus three generous bedrooms & two full baths. The backyard is an entertainers paradise with multiple lounging & dining areas, covered outdoor kitchen with grill, fridge, TV, a Bocce Ball court, trampoline, & fire pit. The resort-style saltwater pool features waterfalls, an extended tanning ledge with fountains, & an oversized hot tub. A stately stone cabana with vaulted cedar ceilings completes the picture. Additional highlights: Sonos system inside & out, mosquito misting system, designer lighting, second staircase near kitchen, custom millwork & closet systems throughout. Roof & gutters, 2019. Both water heaters, 2024. A rare opportunity for luxury living at its finest.

text: This timeless masterpiece in Southlake is truly a dream property, set on an expansive acre of land. It features 6 bedrooms, including 4 conveniently located on the first floor, and 6 full baths along with 2 half baths. An exquisite office on the first floor with a fireplace adds elegance, while the bar area enhances entertainment options. The antique marble fireplace and custom leaded glass leading into the family room provide classic charm. The family room boasts sliding doors that open to an amazing outdoor living space, complete with a stunning pool featuring a child safety electronic cover, multiple outdoor fireplaces, and a complete outdoor kitchen. The huge primary suite on the first floor includes an office, sitting area, and a washer-dryer in the primary closet, along with a spa-like primary bath featuring a steam shower. Indoor entertainment options include a media room equipped with a golf simulator, a gun range simulator, and a game room. Retractable screens for the patio enhance outdoor enjoyment. Additionally, the home comes with a 4-car garage and an impressive almost 800 sq ft shop (not included in size of home) that is temperature controlled, has an electric car charger, and is framed for an RV garage door, allowing for various options including a man cave or even a basketball court. The attention to fine details throughout the home makes it a standout property in a prime location. The home was completed in 2024 and has no HOA.

text: Located in the heart of the highly coveted Cross Timber Hills neighborhood with its charming country atmosphere and no mandatory HOA, this acre plus lot feels spacious, serene, and park-like with its mature trees, a pristine lawn and space for more add-on projects. A two-year project in the making, Ten Bar Trail was reconceptualized with a modern and functional new floor plan, with 90% of this single-story home rebuilt top to bottom using nothing but the finest choices in products and finishes. Very little remains of the original 1984 construction. Daily living has been maximized through efficient space planning while keeping entertaining needs front and center through the ease of flow through the massive kitchen, dining, and great room seating areas. The skys the limit for additional customization in a large second living area. Perfect for a game or media room space, this area would also suit those who need a multi-generational spaceit's split from the owner's suite and could easily accommodate an additional kitchen and second primary bedroom suite. A home office and a workout room that could also be a fourth bedroom are just off this living area. The spacious laundry wasn't skipped in finish, it's finished as finely as the rest of the home. While accessible through the spare bedroom wing, it also connects to the elegant, custom-built primary closet-which then leads to the primary bedroom and bath quarters. With access to the extended covered patio and beautiful view of the pool and backyard, the primary suite is a relaxing retreat where you'll feel close to nature and be enveloped in elegance. Out back you'll find a four-car garage with an attached art studio complete with sink and custom cabinetry. The art studio and east garage are climate-controlled with Daikin mini split systems, while the west garage is fitted with tons of custom storage cabinets, and the entire building is fully insulated. Lot irrigation is supplied by your own well and storage tank.
